WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:02.733
Xiaohui, how are you feeling now?

2
00:00:02.733 --> 00:00:04.300
Is there any discomfort?

3
00:00:04.466 --> 00:00:05.566
Except for the wound, it hurts a little bit.

4
00:00:05.566 --> 00:00:06.666
Nothing else

5
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:09.033
That's good, that's good.

6
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:11.333
Hey, what about mom and sister?

7
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:12.400
The company has a lot of things to do.

8
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.533
Your dad is tired after a busy day

9
00:00:14.533 --> 00:00:16.666
I asked him to take them home to rest

10
00:00:17.266 --> 00:00:18.100
Is your dad now?

11
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:19.700
I finally accepted it one by one.

12
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:22.866
I want to give them a chance to be alone

13
00:00:22.866 --> 00:00:24.200
Develop a relationship

14
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.166
You old fox, it's been a busy day

15
00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:32.066
Aren't you tired?

16
00:00:32.066 --> 00:00:34.966
The old fox is tired

17
00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:35.900
You can't get enough

18
00:00:36.266 --> 00:00:38.700
You just keep feeding haha

19
00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:44.166
Yes, yes, you should let them cultivate it.

20
00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:47.700
Hey, Mom, what about that wild girl Li Hongni?

21
00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.600
Is he dead? Not yet.

22
00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:50.966
But soon.

23
00:00:50.966 --> 00:00:53.400
I heard from the doctor that I only have three days to live

24
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:54.366
Three days.

25
00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.466
So before he died

26
00:00:57.466 --> 00:00:59.266
I can still have some fun with him

